import java.util.Scanner;

public class RepeatingBreakingAndRemembering {
    public static void main(String[] args){
        Scanner scan = new Scanner(System.in);

    }
}


Objective
---------
1st Part:
Write a program to ask for numbers until -1 is entered then it ends.

2nd Part:
Add functionality so that it calculates and prints the sum of numbers entered.

3rd Part:
Add functionality so that it calculates and prints the number of numbers entered.

4th Part:
Add functionality so that it calculates the average of the numbers entered.

5th Part:
Add functionality so that it prints the total number of even and odd numbers entered.